  <!-- intake style form box -->

  <body class="h-screen overflow-hidden font-Inconsolata flex items-center justify-center" style="background: #edf2f7;">

    <div class="w-full max-w-6xl min-w-0 mx-auto px-6 pt-10">
      <div class="flex mt-12 bg-white rounded-md shadow">
        <div class="w-64 bg-black rounded-l-md border-r border-dashed border-white">
          <div
            class="flex justify-center items-center h-32 text-black-700 bg-black text-center font-semibold text-3xl italic">
            <img src="greenCat.png" width=125px class="pt-8">
          </div>
          <div class="mt-8 border-t border-white" >
            <a href="#" onclick="openIntro(event)" class="block text-lg bg-black py-3 px-6 text-white font-semibold border-b border-white" id="mission" >
              Introduction
            </a>
            <a href="/profile" class="block py-3 text-lg px-6 bg-gray-800 text-white font-semibold border-b border-white"
              id="form">
              Submit a habit
            </a>
            <a href="/profile/dashboard" class="block text-lg bg-black py-3 px-6 text-white font-semibold border-b border-white" id="results">
              Go to dashboard
            </a>
            <a href="/profile/texts" class="block text-lg bg-black py-3 px-6 text-white font-semibold border-b border-white" id="texts">
              Get text alerts
            </a>
            <a href="/trackMiles" class="block text-lg bg-black py-3 px-6 text-white font-semibold border-b border-white" id="track">
              Track your miles
            </a>
            <button href="/shareCalendar/<%= userId %>" class="block bg-black py-3 px-6 text-lg text-white font-semibold border-b border-white" class="share" onclick="openWindow(event)">
              Share your calendar
            </button>
          </div>
          <img src="hooked.png" class="p-3 pt-10">
        </div>
        <div class="flex-grow"> 
          <br>
          <h2 class="welcomeTo font-londrina pb-8 font-semibold text-yellow text-4xl px-10">Welcome, <%= email %>!</h2>

          <div class="replace flex flex-col mx-40 mt-15">

            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <form method="post" action="/intakeHabit">
                <label for="habit" class="w-24 font-semibold text-black-700 pr-12">Habit</label>
                <input type="text" name="habit" class="border-double border-4 border-black rounded py-1 px-3"
                  placeholder="name of first habit" />
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <label for="cost" class="w-24 font-semibold text-black-700">Weekly spending <br>on habit</label>
              <input type="number" name="cost" class="border-double border-4 border-black rounded py-1 px-3"
                placeholder="if applicable" />
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <label for="reward" class="w-24 font-semibold text-black-700">Personal Reward</label>
              <input type="text" name="reward" class="border-double border-4 border-black rounded py-1 px-3"
                placeholder="one reward per habit" />
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <textarea name="extraNotes" placeholder="(optional) add an affirmation you want to give to future you"
                class=" mt-4  flex-grow border double-border border-black rounded py-1 px-4" id="description"
                rows="8"></textarea>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <button
                class="submit py-1 px-4 bg-black text-white text-xl font-semibold hover:bg-black-900 hover:shadow border border-black-200 rounded mr-2 mb-3">Submit</button>
              </form>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- The Share Cal Modal -->
<div id="myModal" class="modal">
  <!-- Modal content -->
  <div class="modal-content">
    <span class="close">&times;</span><br>
    <h2 class="copied">Url copied!</h2><br>
   <p class="note"><span style="color:rgb(119, 63, 223)">
     Note:</span> you are entitled to privacy, so when you send this link to your friends or accountability circle, be assured that we removed the ability for your friends to check on your daily activity. With this feature, they will just see your entire calendar activity.</p><br>
     <button><a href="/shareCalendar/<%= userId %>" class="preview">preview what they see >> </a></button> 
  
</div>
</div>
 <!-- End of Share Cal Modal -->

 <!-- The Intro Modal -->
<div id="introModal" class="modal">
  <!-- Modal content -->
  <div class="intro-content">
    <span class="exit">&times;</span><br>
    <h2 class="what-is-this">What is this app?</h2><br>
   <p class="note"><span style="color:rgb(119, 63, 223)">
     Hey, <%= email %>!</span> Great question. This app was created for those who need support to strengthen their skills in breaking what they consider to be bad habits. Oftentimes we talk about people who engage with bad habits as 'lazy' or indulgent. When really, refraining from your bad habits is one of the most challenging, hardest work a person can commit to. Because not everyone's experience is the same, this app has a lot of optional features! If your journey includes exercise, we have a feature to help you see your progress. For users who need an accountability boost, you can sign up for reminder texts, and you can share your calendar with friends. For the visual people, we have a dashboard of data we tracked for you. This app isn't designed to make your journey perfect, but it is designed to help you get stronger. <span style="color:rgb(119, 63, 223)">Thanks!</span></p><br>
  
</div>
</div>
 <!-- End of Intro Modal -->
 

